Name: Turkmenistan 1 Month Multiple Entry Visa
                Visiting Country: Turkmenistan
                Description: Turkmenistan Tourist and Business visa is required for Indian passport holders.
 Processing time is approximate 10 Working days and 1-3 Working days for Urgent Visa

                Visa Fees: USD 135

                Visa Needed: 1
                Type: Tourist
                Documents Required: 1. One (1) Visa Application per person;

2. Passport and its copy as described above;

3. One (1) passport size photo glued to the Application;

4. Fees;

5. Visa Verification Number or Certified Letter of Invitation; 

6. Original HIV/AIDS Certificate, if needed. 

7. Resident Alien Identity Card if required.

